    in the United States
This part of the document integrates with and supplements the information contained in the rest of the privacy policy and is provided by the business running Forest (Android version) and, if the case may be, its parent, subsidiaries and affiliates (for the purposes of this section referred to collectively as “we”, “us”, “our”).
The information contained in this section applies to all Users (Users are referred to below, simply as “you”, “your”, “yours”), who are residents in the following states:
